Q26. What happens as the hot water goes through the radiator?
Q27. What happens to the cool water after it is cooled down?
Ans: IT IS SENT THROUGH THE RADIATOR, WHICH HAS COOL AIR BLOWING THROUGH AND COOLING THE WATER DOWN. THE COOL WATER IS THEN BROUGHT BACK TO THE CPU, RESTARTING THE CYCLE.
